LocLongDescription="You can fire or overwatch with your <Ability:WeaponName/> as a single action with a <Ability:ToHit:ShadowOps_SnapShotShot/> Aim penalty."
LocHelpText="Fire your <Ability:WeaponName/> as a single action with a small Aim penalty."
LocFlyOverText="Snap Shot"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/> Snap Shot is most useful on Hunters that move with the rest of the squad rather than staying in a single place.<br/><Bullet/> Your sniper rifle has an aim penalty at close range. A sword attack will usually be more effective than a close-range flank shot.<br/>"

