[ShadowOps_HunterMark X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Mark"
LocLongDescription="Mark a target, giving all friendly units <Ability:+ToHit/> Aim on shots against it. The bonus never expires, but you can only have one target Marked at a time. Using this ability will not break concealment. <Ability:SelfCooldown/> turn cooldown."
LocHelpText="Mark a target, giving all friendly units <Ability:+ToHit/> Aim on shots against it."
LocFlyOverText="Mark"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/>Mark provides a useful second action on turns where you have to move or reload your sniper rifle.<br/><Bullet/> Use Mark on dangerous enemies before triggering an ambush.<br/><Bullet/> Mark followed by Snap Shot is more accurage than a standard sniper rifle shot, and also helps the rest of the squad.<br/><Bullet/> Mark can target using squadsight.<br/><Bullet/> Marking does not break concealment.<br/><Bullet/> The effect is removed if the Hunter dies, evacs, or marks another target.<br/><Bullet/> Mark has a <Ability:SelfCooldown/> turn cooldown.<br/>"

[ShadowOps_VitalPoint X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Keen Edge"
LocLongDescription="Your sword attacks shred <Ability:Shred/> armor and deal <Ability:+Damage/> damage."
LocHelpText="Your sword attacks shred <Ability:Shred/> armor and deal <Ability:+Damage/> damage."
LocFlyOverText="Keen Edge"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/> More advanced swords will shred more armor and deal extra bonus damage.<br/><Bullet/> Your sword attacks can finish off a wounded enemy and move to a better position for using your sniper rifle at the same time.<br/><Bullet/> Because of the Hunter's high Aim stat, your sword attacks will almost always hit.<br/><Bullet/> Keen Edge will make a normal sword deal as much damage as a sniper rifle of the same tech tier.<br/>"

[ShadowOps_Precision X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Precision"
LocLongDescription="You get <Ability:+ToHit/> Aim against targets in full cover."
LocHelpText="You get <Ability:+ToHit/> Aim against targets in full cover."
LocFlyOverText="Precision"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/> Precision only works with ranged attacks.<br/>"

[ShadowOps_LowProfile X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Low Profile"
LocLongDescription="You get <Ability:+Defense/> Defense while in half cover."
LocHelpText="You get <Ability:+Defense/> Defense while in half cover."
LocFlyOverText="Low Profile"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/> The bonus is lost if the attacker is flanking you.<br/>"

[ShadowOps_Sprint X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Sprint"
LocLongDescription="Gain a bonus move action this turn. <Ability:SelfCooldown/> turn cooldown."
LocHelpText="Gain a bonus move action this turn."
LocFlyOverText="Sprint"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/> Sprint can be used to move very long distances in a single turn, or to move and then take a normal sniper rifle shot.<br/><Bullet/> The extra move action from Sprint is wasted if you use an ability that ends your turn, like firing your weapon, before taking the move.<br/><Bullet/> Sprint has a <Ability:SelfCooldown/> turn cooldown.<br/>"

[ShadowOps_Assassin X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Assassin"
LocLongDescription="When you kill a flanked or uncovered enemy with your <Ability:WeaponName/>, you gain concealment."
LocHelpText="When you kill a flanked or uncovered enemy with your <Ability:WeaponName/>, you gain concealment."
LocFlyOverText="Assassin"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/> You must have cover from all enemies that can see you in order to gain the concealment.<br/>"

[ShadowOps_Fade X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Fade"
LocLongDescription="Gain concealment that is broken if you move. <Ability:SelfCooldown/> turn cooldown."
LocHelpText="Gain concealment that is broken if you move."
LocFlyOverText="Fade"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/> Fade will let you use your First Strike bonus multiple times during a battle.<br/><Bullet/> Concealment granted by Fade can also be broken normally.<br/><Bullet/> Fade consumes an action and has a <Ability:SelfCooldown/> turn cooldown.<br/>"

[ShadowOps_SliceAndDice X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Slice and Dice"
LocLongDescription="Attack any enemy within movement range with your sword. If you hit, make a free second sword attack. <Ability:SelfCooldown/> turn cooldown."
LocHelpText="Attack any enemy within movement range with your sword. If you hit, make a free second sword attack."
LocFlyOverText="Slice and Dice"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/> Slice and Dice has a <Ability:SelfCooldown/> turn cooldown.<br/>"

[ShadowOps_Tracking X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Tracking"
LocLongDescription="You detect nearby units even without line of sight."
LocHelpText="You detect nearby units even without line of sight."
LocFlyOverText="Tracking"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/> Soldiers with Tracking make excellent scouts, especially if you give them concealment with Stealth Protocol.<br/><Bullet/> Tracking detects enemies slightly, but only slightly, outside normal visual range.<br/><Bullet/> Tracking will reveal concealed and burrowed enemies. <br/>"

[ShadowOps_TrackingTrigger X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Tracking"
LocFlyOverText="Tracking"

[ShadowOps_Bullseye X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Bullseye"
LocLongDescription="Fire a shot that deals critical damage and gives the target penalties to Aim, Defense, and Will. <Ability:SelfCooldown/> turn cooldown."
LocHelpText="Fire a shot that deals critical damage and gives the target penalties to Aim, Defense, and Will."
LocFlyOverText="Bullseye"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/> Bullseye is good for weakening tough enemies while also dealing extra damage.<br/><Bullet/> Bullseye applies -20 penalties to Aim, Defense, and Will that last until the end of the battle. <br/><Bullet/> Bullseye has a <Ability:SelfCooldown/> turn cooldown. <br/>"

[ShadowOps_FirstStrike X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="First Strike"
LocLongDescription="While concealed or flanking your target, you deal <Ability:+Damage/> damage with your <Ability:WeaponName/> and take no penalties from using Squadsight."
LocHelpText="While concealed or flanking your target, you deal <Ability:+Damage/> damage with your <Ability:WeaponName/> and take no penalties from using Squadsight."
LocFlyOverText="First Strike"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/> First Strike can provide a decisive advantage in an ambush by taking out a tough enemy in one shot.<br/><Bullet/> The soldier with First Strike must initiate the ambush to get the bonus. It doesn't affect concealed overwatch."

[ShadowOps_DamnGoodGround X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Damn Good Ground"
LocLongDescription="You get an additional <Ability:+ToHit/> Aim and <Ability:+Defense/> Defense against targets at lower elevation."
LocHelpText="You get an additional <Ability:+ToHit/> Aim and <Ability:+Defense/> Defense against targets at lower elevation."
LocFlyOverText="Damn Good Ground"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/> The bonus stacks with the normal Aim bonus for higher elevation.<br/>"

[ShadowOps_PointBlank X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Hipfire"
LocLongDescription="Reduces the Aim penalty for short-range sniper rifle shots by 67%."
LocHelpText="Reduces the Aim penalty for short-range sniper rifle shots by 67%."
LocFlyOverText="Hipfire"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/> Hipfire reduces the maximum range penalty for a short-range sniper rifle shot from -30 to -10.<br/><Bullet/> Hipfire does not affect the aim penalty from Snap Shot.<br/>"

[ShadowOps_Butcher X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Butcher"
LocLongDescription="Increases damage against organic targets by 30%."
LocHelpText="Increases damage against organic targets by 30%."
LocFlyOverText="Butcher"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/> Organic targets means all non-mechanical units.<br/>"

[ShadowOps_Reposition X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Reposition"
LocLongDescription="You can take a standard move action after firing your <Ability:WeaponName/>."
LocHelpText="Fire your <Ability:WeaponName/> at a target, then move."
LocFlyOverText="Reposition"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/> Reposition only allows standard moves, not other abilities such as reloading your weapon.<br/>"

[ShadowOps_Evasive X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Sixth Sense"
LocLongDescription="You are immune to multi-target and area attacks."
LocHelpText="You are immune to multi-target and area attacks."
LocFlyOverText="Sixth Sense"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/> Area attacks include grenades and other explosives.<br/>"

[ShadowOps_Stalker X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Stalker"
LocLongDescription="Gain <Ability:+Mobility/> Mobility and <Ability:+ToHit/> Aim while concealed."
LocHelpText="Gain <Ability:+Mobility/> Mobility and <Ability:+ToHit/> Aim while concealed."
LocFlyOverText="Stalker"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/> The bonuses are lost immediately when you lose concealment.<br/>"

[ShadowOps_LastStand X2AbilityTemplate]
LocFriendlyName="Last Stand"
LocLongDescription="Once per mission, become immune to death and incapacitation until the end of your next turn."
LocHelpText="Become immune to death and incapacitation until the end of your next turn."
LocFlyOverText="Last Stand"
LocPromotionPopupText="<Bullet/> You can still take damage, but it will never reduce you below 1 hp.<br/><Bullet/> You can't be knocked unconscious, disoriented, or otherwise incapacitated.<br/>"

